iscoveries and knowledge systems.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aJohn Donne, physics, science, medicine, poetics, devotions, soul.1 aHarrison, Timothy M., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226833521423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226833521/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles